118
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:24,270
What should I do now?

119
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:47,790
I-I don't understand...
What happened, Yoshikage?

120
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:51,510
You've been acting strange since last night.

121
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,060
Listen to me, Yoshikage!

122
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:59,990
That Rohan Kishibe has started investigating
Hayato Kawajiri for some reason!

123
00:08:59,990 --> 00:09:03,580
They're going to come
check this house tomorrow.

124
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:06,400
There's no need to worry.

125
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:09,230
B-But, Yoshikage!

126
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:15,830
Deadly Queen has gained a third ability.

127
00:09:22,660 --> 00:09:24,250
I... I don't understand.

128
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:29,420
What could have happened
to make you so carefree?

129
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,950
Miso-stewed Cow Tongue

130
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,950
-Morioh's Very Own-

131
00:09:29,690 --> 00:09:31,360
Miso-stewed cow tongue.

132
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:37,770
What? No way! We're on the air already?

133
00:09:38,490 --> 00:09:43,720
Er, um... It's now 7:55, so here's
the weather today for the prefecture.

134
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,940
Today should be sunny.

135
00:09:46,940 --> 00:09:51,060
Hayato! Hey, Hayato! Answer the phone.

136
00:09:53,020 --> 00:09:57,090
After that bath last night, he changed.

137
00:09:57,090 --> 00:09:59,480
Wh-What could have happened?

138
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:05,910
Hayato! I asked you to answer the phone!

139
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:08,860
Crash

140
00:10:10,410 --> 00:10:12,380
My precious tea set!

141
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,080
This is all your fault!

142
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:18,260
Why do you always ignore me?!

143
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:21,720
Fine! You think your mother's
just a bother, right?!

144
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,590
Do whatever you want, then!

145
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:28,390
Now, now. Let's not fight
first thing in the morning.

146
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:31,520
If it broke, I'll just buy you another one.

147
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:34,650
Hello, Kawajiri residence.

148
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,790
No, it's not.

149
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,660
They had the wrong number.

150
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:43,670
Hayato's just at an age where
he doesn't want to talk much.

151
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:49,320
We're family, so we all need to get along.

152
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,640
You know, get along.

153
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,500
Well, I'll head off to work now.

154
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:57,270
Do you mind if I give you a goodbye kiss?

155
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,260
Huh?

156
00:10:58,700 --> 00:11:00,050
I'll be off now.

157
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,890
H-He left...

158
00:11:21,890 --> 00:11:23,820
No, I'm right here.

159
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:27,400
Why don't we walk together part of the way?

160
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:38,090
Going from feeling refreshed
to falling into despair...

161
00:11:38,090 --> 00:11:43,050
So much has happened lately.
I've been on an emotional roller coaster.

162
00:11:43,590 --> 00:11:48,500
But now I'll be able to feel at ease.

163
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:53,010
Since you cornered me last
night, I was able to mature.

164
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:58,800
Really, your will last night was so strong.

165
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:02,230
To think that you would actually turn
around and threaten me, Yoshikage Kira...

166
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:05,620
Y-Yoshikage Kira?

167
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,620
Did I just say my real name?

168
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:11,180
A-Are you planning to kill me after all?

169
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:12,380
Kill you?

170
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:14,800
Because you found out my secret?

171
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:18,630
There's no need for that.
Because I've matured.

172
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:21,660
No matter where you go and
what you do with anyone,

173
00:12:21,660 --> 00:12:23,930
it doesn't matter, because
now, none can rival me.

174
00:12:24,930 --> 00:12:29,310
I have no interest in you anymore.
If I wanted to kill you...

175
00:12:30,110 --> 00:12:32,770
I would have gotten rid of you last night.

176
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:36,770
From now on, we're all going to get
along and live happily together.

177
00:12:36,770 --> 00:12:39,970
So just relax... Like we're family.

178
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:43,490
Well, I have to head to the station.

179
00:12:43,490 --> 00:12:46,490
Make sure you study hard, Hayato.

180
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:54,890
Rival... He just said none can rival him...

181
00:12:54,890 --> 00:12:57,010
Which means there must be others

182
00:12:57,010 --> 00:13:00,590
that have the same kind of abilities as him.

183
00:13:00,590 --> 00:13:03,750
