above the Pepsi sign.

239
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:28,190
8:27...

240
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:39,200
Wh-Who in the world is this Hayato Kawajiri?

241
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:41,370
Why is he experiencing things in the future?

242
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:44,580
Could he be a Stand user?

243
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:51,580
No... This is too odd to be a Stand ability.

244
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:53,500
All I can read with Heaven's Door

245
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:55,760
is what he has personally seen or heard.

246
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:58,880
The answer to this should
be written somewhere...

247
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:01,290
My dad isn't my dad

248
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:03,010
He made a man and a woman disappear at an apartment in Jozenji by making them explode.

249
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:04,510
He's a murderer. I found out who
he was. He has inhuman abilities.

250
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,010
My dad's name is Yoshikage Kira

251
00:16:07,010 --> 00:16:08,030
Yoshikage Kira

252
00:16:08,470 --> 00:16:09,690
Kira...

253
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,410
I-I did it!

254
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:19,590
This kid was the jackpot!

255
00:16:19,590 --> 00:16:21,080
I finally found him!

256
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:24,030
Yoshikage Kira is Kosaku Kawajiri!

